{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"syntax":null,"type":"codeListing","code":[" If a text's language supports horizontal writing mode, symbols with point"," placement would be laid out horizontally."]}]}],"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"case","roleHeading":"Enumeration Case","externalID":"c:@E@MLNTextWritingMode@MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal"}]},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNTextWritingMode"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The property allows control over a symbol’s orientation. Note that the property","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"values act as a hint, so that a symbol whose language doesn’t support the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"provided orientation will be laid out in its natural orientation. Example:","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"English point symbol will be rendered horizontally even if array value contains","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"single ‘vertical’ enum value. The order of elements in an array define priority","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"order for the placement of an orientation variant.","type":"text"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode","title":"MLNTextWritingMode"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNTextWritingMode/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNTextWritingMode\/MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlntextwritingmode\/mlntextwritingmodehorizontal","fragments":[{"text":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[],"title":"MLNTextWritingModeHorizontal","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","title":"MapLibre"}}}